# End of every response — mandatory context report

Every response must end with this block (no exceptions, for ALL agents):

```
READ: <comma-separated list of every file and artifact you read this turn>
TOKENS_EST: ~<sum of file sizes / 4>
```

Example:
```
READ: artifacts/_index.md, artifacts/modules/main.json, src/main.py
TOKENS_EST: ~1240
```

Rules for the report:
- List EVERY file read this turn — source files, artifacts, rules, anything
- Estimate tokens as: sum of file sizes in bytes ÷ 4
- If you read no files, write: READ: none · TOKENS_EST: ~0
- Do NOT skip this block even for short responses

After the report, add:

> Done. Review the result — continue, fix something specific, or close the task?
